title.rendered: STEDI Square Type USB Charger Switch Insert

content.rendered:
Toyota Square USB Charger Switch OEM Style

DETAILS

STEDI’s new 5V 2.1A USB charger insert, with an ice blue, LED backlight.

COMPATIBLE TOYOTA MAKES

  • Toyota Prado 150 Series | 2018 – Onward
  • Fits STEDI 70 series/Ford Ranger custom STEDI switch fascia

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Ice Blue
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 22x22mm
RATED 5V @ 2.1A

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1 x  22 x 22mm Square Type USB Charger
